There was one other sighting in Merriam on or around May 26th 2011
Summary: granddaughter,10, looked out back window & saw dark, triangular object with lights
divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving home from Iowa to Merriam,KS. with my granddaughter, 10, in the backseat, right side; it was just the two of us. I was going south on 635, right before it turns into Metcalf, crossing over I-35 and she said "I see something above the highway", I-35, and told me it was a triangle with lights, dark in color; was stationary when she saw it. I could not turn around and look myself because of the traffic. This occurred approx. 6:30 pm on Thursday 5-26-11
